# Versioning Before Release

When template behavior changes in a release, update project versioning deliberately.

## Rules

- Use semantic versioning for template releases.
- Update `CHANGELOG.md` when user-facing behavior changes.
- Do not bundle unrelated changes in the same release/version bump.

## For apps created from this template

- Carry versioning policy into the app repo.
- If the app is deployed/published, keep changelog and version in sync with releases.
